## Project Goal

The objective of this project was to create an engaging, interactive self-reflection experience that encourages users to better understand their decision-making patterns in a thoughtful and approachable way.

Instead of functioning as a personality or psychological assessment, the application promotes curiosity, exploration, and personal insight through interactive storytelling and game-like mechanics.

